0of%20a%2090-hour%20workweek.%20In%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20he%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9C90%20hours%20a%20week%3F%20Why%20not%20rename%20Sunday%20to%20%E2%80%98Sun-duty'%20and%20make%20%E2%80%98day%20off'%20a%20mythical%20concept!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20Congress%20Chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20joined%20the%20conversation%2C%20opposing%20the%20suggestion%20of%20excessively%20long%20working%20hours.%20He%20invoked%20the%20principles%20of%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20and%20Dr%20BR%20Ambedkar%2C%20who%20had%20strongly%20advocated%20limiting%20workers%20to%20an%20eight-hour%20workday.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737115920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-10%2Fs6ofk9h8_infosys-ceo-salil-parekh-650_650x400_22_October_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finfosys-ceo-salil-parekh-addresses-toxic-work-culture-charge-committed-to-fairness-7495033%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Infosys%20CEO%20Salil%20Parekh%20addressed%20toxic%20work%20culture%20allegations%20during%20the%20companys%20Q3%20earnings%20call%20on%20January%2016.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20huge%20fire%20broke%20out%20at%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20battery%20storage%20plants%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228256%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Fire%20erupted%20at%20Moss%20Landing%20Power%20Plant%20on%20Thursday%20in%20Moss%20Landing%20of%20Monterey%20Bay%2C%20California%2C%20on%20January%2017%2C%202025.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678a39092fcded5e90739d39%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20fire%20erupted%20at%20Moss%20Landing%20Power%20Plant%20in%20California%20on%20January%2017%2C%202025.%3Cp%3ETayfun%20Coskun%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E