%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FauqikEHZKz%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FauqikEHZKz%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Saad%20Kaiser%20%F0%9F%87%B5%F0%9F%87%B0%20(%40TheSaadKaiser)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTheSaadKaiser%2Fstatus%2F1687062159917039616%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%203%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20was%20so%20special%20about%20the%20watch%3F%20The%20diamond-dotted%20Graff%20had%20a%20Khana-e-Kaaba%20watchface.%20It's%20a%20dazzling%20thing%20of%20beauty%20that%20you%20cannot%20comprehend%20the%20price%20of.%20The%20token%20of%20goodwill%20from%20MBS%20brought%20home%20a%20lot%20of%20badwill%20for%20Khan.%20These%20were%20gifts%20meant%20for%20the%20Pakistan%20state.%20Khan%2C%20as%20the%20guardian%20of%20the%20state%2C%20was%20supposed%20to%20guard%20the%20gifts%20that%20the%20state%20received.%20Khan%20did%20not.%20He%20sold%20the%20watch.%20You%20cannot%20sell%20a%20watch%20that's%20the%20only%20one%20in%20the%20world%20and%20not%20get%20caught.%20So%2C%20Khan%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Saga%20Of%20Shame%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20centre%20of%20this%20potboiler%20of%20shame%20is%20a%20Dubai-based%20businessman%20called%20Umar%20Farooq%20Zahoor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZahoor%20has%20an%20affinity%20for%20unique%20timepieces.%20He%20is%20a%20collector%20and%20connoisseur%20of%20watches.%20So%2C%20he%20lapped%20up%20the%20idea%20of%20owning%20a%20piece%20as%20unique%20as%20the%20Khana-e-Kaaba%20Graff%20watch.%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20through%20his%20wife%20Bushra%20Bibi%2C%20struck%20a%20deal.%20Zahoor%20claimed%20in%20a%202023%20interview%20to%20%3Cem%3EGeo%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Khan%20sold%20the%20Graff%20custom%20set%20to%20him%20via%20an%20intermediary%20named%20Farah%20Gogi.%20Gogi%20was%20Bushra's%20closest%20friend%20and%20companion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EHow%20Imran%20Khan%20sold%20the%20rare%20Graff%20watch%20to%20me%20in%20Dubai.%20I%20reveal%20in%20my%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSaleemKhanSafi%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40SaleemKhanSafi%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20broadcast%20on%20Geo%20News.%20Role%20of%20Farah%20Gogi%2C%20Shahzad%20Akbar%20and%20the%20former%20First%20Lady%20explained%20and%20why%20Shahzad%20Akbar%20made%20fake%20cases%20on%20me.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FaldvnU0WEt%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FaldvnU0WEt%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Umar%20Farooq%20Zahoor%20(%40UmarFaroqZahoor)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUmarFaroqZahoor%2Fstatus%2F1686438251811262464%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%201%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Bushra%2C%20the%20Graff%20was%20a%20watch.%20A%20very%20expensive%20watch%2C%20but%20just%20a%20watch.%20So%2C%20the%20nuance%20and%20the%20detailing%20and%20the%20uniqueness%20of%20the%20Khana-e-Kaaba%20timepiece%20did%20not%20quite%20penetrate%20Bushra's%20veil%2C%20and%20the%20transfer%20took%20place%20in%20Dubai.%20Zahoor%20apparently%20paid%20%2412%20million%20for%20the%20Graff%20set.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Man%20Who%20Wouldn't%20Stay%20Quiet%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Graff%20set%20came%20into%20his%20possession%2C%20Zahoor%20did%20not%20sit%20quiet.%20He%20went%20about%20town%20claiming%20that%20he%20was%20the%20proud%20owner%20of%20a%20watch%20that%20was%20the%20only%20one%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20where%20did%20it%20all%20fall%20apart%20for%20Khan%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20begin%20with%2C%20the%20watch%20wasn't%20his%20to%20sell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20it%20was%20a%20watch%20that%20was%20as%20easily%20traceable%20as%20contrast%20dye%20in%20your%20MRI.%20It%20was%20the%20only%20one%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Saudis%20weren't%20happy.%20Mohammed%20Bin%20Salman%20was%20furious%20to%20see%20the%20Khana-e-Kaaba%20sold%20for%20profit.%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20relation%20with%20Pakistan%20wasn't%20for%20sale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20Imran%20Khan%20saw%20his%20world%20crumbling%20as%20the%20Toshakhana%20case%20grabbed%20him%20by%20the%20throat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETale%20Of%20The%20Toshakhana%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan's%20Toshakhana%20(Treasury)%20rules%20state%20that%20government%20officials%20can%20keep%20state%20gifts%20as%20long%20as%20they%20pay%20for%20them.%20But%2C%20the%20gifts%20need%20to%20be%20deposited%20first.%20The%20Toshakhana%20is%20the%20department%20under%20the%20Cabinet%20Division%20which%20keeps%20all%20state%20gifts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20rules%2C%20Imran%20Khan%20was%20also%20supposed%20to%20have%20deposited%20the%20Graff%20set%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20several%20other%20state%20gifts%20he%20received%2C%20with%20the%20Toshakhana.%20Khan%20did%20not.%20He%20did%20not%20even%20keep%20the%20gifts.%20He%20sold%20them%20off%2C%20much%20to%20the%20chagrin%20of%20the%20states%20that%20gifted%20the%20gifts%20to%20Khan.%20MBS%20was%20on%20top%20of%20that%20list.%20Graff%20perhaps%20came%20a%20close%20second%2C%20at%20seeing%20itself%20dragged%20into%20this%20saga%20of%20ignominy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Graff%20Galaxy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGraff%2C%20high%20jewellery%20makers%20since%201962%2C%20are%20famous%20with%20just%20about%20anyone%20who's%20anyone%20in%20the%20world.%20The%20house%20prides%20itself%20on%20showmanship.%20Their%20diamonds%20are%20arguably%20the%20best%20in%20the%20world%2C%20straight%20off%20the%20mineowner-founder's%20knowledge%20of%20the%20stone.%20Most%20of%20its%20high%20jewellery%20collection%20is%20priced%20upwards%20of%20%24100%2C000.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Star%20of%20Bombay%2C%20acquired%20by%20Laurence%20Graff%20in