ucation%20Ministry%20-%20in%20committees%20to%20appoint%20vice-chancellors%20for%20state-run%20universities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20says%20these%20universities'%20statutes%20do%20not%20allow%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20moved%20the%20court%20last%20year%20after%20Mr%20Ravi%20set%20up%20a%20committee%20to%20name%20vice-chancellors%20for%20the%20University%20of%20Madras%2C%20Bharathiar%20University%2C%20and%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Teachers%20Training%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20called%20the%20move%20%26quot%3Billegal%26quot%3B%20and%20reconstituted%20the%20committee%2C%20removing%20members%20from%20the%20University%20Grants%20Commission%2C%20a%20statutory%20body%20under%20the%20Union%20Education%20Ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftamil-nadu-news%2Ftamil-nadu-governor-rn-ravi-withdraws-notification-over-appointment-of-vice-chancellors-4833453%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMr%20Ravi%20later%20withdrew%20the%20search%20committees%20he%20had%20set%20up%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20the%20DMK%20moved%20the%20court%20seeking%20directions%20to%20the%20Governor%20to%20clear%20several%20bills%2C%20including%20two%20passed%20by%20the%20preceding%20All%20India%20Anna%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam-led%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20party%20accused%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-appointed%20Mr%20Ravi%20of%20deliberately%20delaying%20the%20bills%20and%20scuttling%20the%20state's%20development%20by%20%26quot%3Bundermining%20the%20elected%20administration%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftamil-nadu-governor-returns-10-bills-week-after-court-expressed-concerns-4578952%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETamil%20Nadu%20Governor%20Returns%2010%20Bills%2C%20Week%20After%20Court's%20Concerns%3C%2Fa%3E%