%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fmaruti-to-become-largest-electric-car-producer-in-india-in-one-year-md-125011700837_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20stated%20that%20the%20e-Vitara%20will%20first%20be%20exported%20to%20a%20few%20key%20markets%20before%20being%20put%20on%20sale%20in%20India%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fmaruti-to-become-largest-electric-car-producer-in-india-in-one-year-md-125011700837_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20As%20Hindenburg%20Closes%20'Pipeline%20of%20Ideas'%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20Attacks%20'Indian%20State'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHindenburg%2C%20the%20US-based%20predatory%20short-seller%20whose%20research%20caused%20a%20sharp%20decline%20in%20share%20prices%20in%20Indian%20markets%20in%20January%202023%2C%20and%20which%20fuelled%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20Modi-Adani%20propaganda%2C%20shut%20down%20on%20January%2015.%20Its%20founder%2C%20Nathan%20Anderson%2C%20informed%20the%20media%20that%20the%20firm%20had%20%E2%80%9Cfinished%20the%20pipeline%20of%20ideas%E2%80%9D%20it%20was%20working%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Many%20Are%20Panicking%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20closure%20of%20Hindenburg%20is%20seen%20in%20the%20context%20of%20political%20developments%20in%20the%20US.%20With%20the%20inauguration%20of%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20on%20January%2020%20approaching%2C%20panic%20has%20gripped%20institutions%20that%20Trump%20is%20wary%20of.%20Hindenburg%20had%20been%20financed%20by%20George%20Soros%20and%20was%20part%20of%20his%20broader%20influence.%20Trump%20is%20openly%20hostile%20to%20Soros%2C%20the%20Hungarian-born%20multimillionaire%20who%20funds%20NGOs%20in%20over%20120%20countries%20and%20is%20linked%20to%20efforts%20to%20overthrow%20elected%20governments.%20The%20Bangladesh%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Eabhyutthan%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(uprising)%20of%20August%202024%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20instigated%20by%20individuals%20like%20Soros%2C%20according%20to%20some%20within%20the%20US%20deep%20state.%20Sixteen%20days%20before%20leaving%20office%2C%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20awarded%20Soros%20America's%20highest%20civilian%20honour%2C%20the%20Presidential%20Medal%20of%20Freedom%2C%20which%20Trump%20ally%20Elon%20Musk%20called%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctravesty%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Hindenburg's%20%E2%80%9Cpipeline%20of%20ideas%E2%80%9D%20ran%20dry%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20along%20with%20his%20trusted%20spokesman%20Jairam%20Ramesh%2C%20saw%20a%20hole%20in%20their%20Modi-Adani%20narrative.%20In%20response%2C%20Gandhi%20declared%20that%20the%20Congress%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20only%20fighting%20the%20BJP%20%5BBharatiya%20Janata%20Party%5D%C2%A0and%20the%20RSS%20%5BRashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%5D%2C%20but%20also%20fighting%20the%20Indian%20State.%E2%80%9D%20These%20words%20were%20spoken%20during%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20new%20Congress%20Headquarters%2C%20Indira%20Bhawan%2C%20on%20January%2015%E2%80%94just%20hours%20before%20the%20official%20announcement%20of%20Hindenburg's%20closure%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20Hardeep%20Puri%20quickly%20retorted%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20declaration%20of%20war%20on%20the%20Indian%20State%20echoed%20George%20Soros's%20%E2%80%9Ctoolkit%E2%80%9D.%20BJP%20President%20J.P.%20Nadda%20called%20it%20a%20statement%20from%20an%20%E2%80%9Curban%20Naxal%26quot%3B.%20Senior%20journalist%20Pankaj%20Sharma%2C%20speaking%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Congress%20during%20a%20chat%20show%2C%20attempted%20to%20clarify%20that%20Gandhi%20was%20not%20targeting%20the%20Union%20of%20India%20but%20rather%20opposing%20the%20current%20ruling%20dispensation.%20However%2C%20his%20explanation%20sounded%20tenuous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Really%20Is%20A%20State%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Western%20concept%20of%20the%20state%20dates%20back%20to%20the%20Greco-Roman%20era.%20The%20word%20'state'%20is%20derived%20from%20the%20Latin%20'status'%2C%20meaning%20the%20condition%20of%20a%20country.%20In%20ancient%20India%2C%20the%20state%20was%20known%20as%20a%20'Janapada'.%20A%20state%20is%20an%20organised%20political%20community%20under%20the%20control%20of%20a%20single%20government%2C%20characterised%20by%20sovereignty%2C%20defined%20territorial%20boundaries%2C%20and%20governance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20this%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20statement%20that%20his%20party%20is%20%E2%80%9Calso%20fighting%20the%20Indian%20State%E2%80%9D%20raises%20an%20important%20question%3A%20is%20he%20suggesting%20that%20India%20could%20face%20events%20similar%20to%20the%202022%20Sri%20Lankan%20crisis%20or%20the%202024%20Bangladesh%20uprising%3F%20Gandhi%20and%20his%20party%20frequently%20questioned%20the%20electoral%20process%20and%20criticised%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%E2%80%94yet%20both%20charges%20were%20dismissed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20rejected%20petitions%20from%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESimilar%20Comments%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20YouTube%20clip%20shown%20on%20TV%20channels%20in%20mid-December%20highlighted%20the%20striking%20similarity%20between%20the%20statements%20of%20George%20Soros%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20regarding%20India.%20In%20this%20clip%2C%20Soros%20states%20that%20in%20the%20coming%20months%2C%20he%20foresees%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20weakening%20of%20Modi's%20stranglehold%20on%20India's%20federal%20government%2C%20which%20will%20open%20doors%20for%20institutional%20reform%26quot%3B.%20The%20same%20clip%20shows%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20echoing%20Soros's%20words%20at%20a%20party%20meeting%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%3Cem%3Eyeh%20jo%20Narendra%20Modi%20bhashan%20de%20raha%20hai%2C%20main%20aapsey%20kahna%20chahta%20hoon%2C%20chhey-saat%20mahiney%20baad%20yeh%20apne%20ghar%20se%20nahin%20nikal%20paayega.%20Hindustan%20ke%20yuva%20isko%20aisa%20danda%20marenge%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(Modi%20is%20giving%20speeches...%20in%20six-seven%20months%2C%20he%20will%20be%20unable%20to%20leave%20his%20home...%20the%20youth%20of%20India%20will%20hammer%20him).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20kind%20of%20political%20discourse%20has%20reached%20its%20nadir.%20It%20suggests%20violence%20as%20a%20tool%20for%20political%20debate.%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20frustration%20at%20seeing%20Narendra%20Modi%20poised%20for%20a%20third%20term%2C%20despite%20the%20worldwide%20anti-incumbency%20wave%20of%202024%2C%20is%20evident%20in%20statements%20that%20clearly%20do%20not%20align%20with%20the%20legacy%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi's%20party.%20It%20reflects%20a%20departure%20from%20the%20democratic%20ideals%20set%20by%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20Congress%20Stage%20A%20Comeback%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Congress%20enters%20the%20140th%20year%20of%20its%20political%20journey%2C%20despite%20sitting%20in%20the%20opposition%20for%20a%20third%20consecutive%20term%2C%20the%20party%20can%20take%20solace%20in%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20BJP's%20call%20for%20a%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ECongress-mukt%20Bharat'%3C%2Fem%3E%20(India%20sans%20Congress)%20has%20failed.%20The%20Congress%20continues%20to%20hold%20the%20position%20of%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20both%20houses%20of%20Parliament%20and%20remains%20the%20only%20nationwide%20challenger%20to%20the%20BJP.%3Cbr%3E%5CnOut%20of%20the%20543%20seats%20in%20the%20current%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20286%20are%20seeing%20a%20direct%20contest%20between%20the%20two%20national%20parties.%20In%202024%2C%20the%20Congress%20regained%20ground%2C%20winning%2083%20out%20of%20its%2099%20seats%20against%20the%20BJP.%20The%20BJP's%20tally%20of%20240%20included%20180%20wins%20over%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20Congress%20strengthens%20its%20organisational%20base%20and%20the%20BJP's%20fortunes%20take%20a%20hit%2C%20there%20is%20a%20possibility%20for%20the%20Congress%20to%20stage%20a%20comeback%2C%20much%20like%20the%20Labour%20Party%20in%20the%20UK.%20Political%20fortunes%20are%20inherently%20volatile.%20Democratic%20politics%20must%20recognise%20that%20Winston%20Churchill%2C%20despite%20leading%20the%20Allied%20Powers%20to%20victory%20and%20defeating%20the%20Nazis%2C%20lost%20the%20post-war%20elections%20in%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20becoming%20Prime%20Minister%20in%20May%201991%2C%20P.V.%20Narasimha%20Rao%20invited%20national%20editors%20for%20tea.%20This%20writer%20had%20the%20privilege%20of%20attending%20that%20t%C3%AAte-%C3%A0-t%C3%AAte%20at%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20House.%20Rao%2C%20leading%20a%20coalition%20government%2C%20was%20asked%20how%20he%20felt%20about%20assuming%20office.%20He%20replied%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20feel%20like%20a%20batsman%20who's%20on%2099%2C%E2%80%9D%20perhaps%20implying%20that%20his%20sense%20of%20fulfilment%20was%20still%20to%20come.%20A%20score%20of%2099%2C%20thus%2C%20is%20not%20a%20dismal%20one.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20scored%2027%25%E2%80%94well%20behind%20Modi's%2047%25%E2%80%94in%20a%20popularity%20poll%20conducted%20by%20CSDS-Lokniti%20prior%20to%20the%202024%20elections%2C%20should%20not%20despair%20if%20he%20follows%20the%20rules%20and%20refrains%20from%20merely%20displaying%20a%20red%20copy%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shubhabrata%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20retired%20editor%20and%20a%20public%20affairs%20commentator)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737111300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F48268m9_rahul-gandhi_640x480_14_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fas-hindenburg-closes-pipeline-of-ideas-rahul-gandhi-attacks-indian-state-7495517%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20C