ct-yourself-from-hacks-or-scams-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escam-proof%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20was%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228884084f-f264-4a5f-ae8e-47182aadcb8a%5C%22%3EStressful%20travel%20made%20me%20feel%20desperate%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20tail%20end%20of%20spending%20time%20back%20East%20with%20my%20family%2C%20my%20son%20got%20sick%20on%20the%20day%20we%20were%20supposed%20to%20fly%20home%20to%20LA%2C%20so%20I%20delayed%20our%20flight%20for%20two%20days.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fswitching-airlines-on-layover-to-avoid-budget-flight-delays-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplane%20ticket%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20easy%20to%20switch%20with%20no%20extra%20charges%2C%20but%20when%20I%20went%20to%20extend%20my%20rental%20car%2C%20the%20company%20website%20said%20they'd%20charge%20me%20more%20than%20%243%2C000%20for%20a%20rental%20car%20that%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20just%20%2451%20per%20day.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EI%20was%20panicked.%20I%20told%20myself%20this%20must%20be%20a%20mistake%20and%20called%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-chatbots-customer-service-call-center-annoying-problems-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecustomer%20service%20number%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20help.%20After%20an%20hour%20of%20getting%20redirected%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcustomer-service-phone-calls-paid-status-symbol-luxury-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eautomated%20lines%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20and%20over%20I%20felt%20sick.%20I%20couldn't%20pay%20for%20this%20%E2%80%94%20it%20would%20cost%20more%20than%20our%20entire%20trip.%20If%20I%20could%20just%20get%20in%20touch%20with%20a%20live%20person%2C%20I%20had%20hope%20that%20everything%20could%20be%20worked%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22573abd09-a595-4173-b012-67584a94ac82%5C%22%3E%3Cbr%3EI%20turned%20to%20social%20media%20for%20help%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20remembered%20I%20had%20had%20luck%20contacting%20corporations%20through%20social%20media%20before%20and%20found%20the%20rental%20company's%20official%20Facebook%20page.%20I%20posted%20a%20message%20about%20my%20situation%20with%20a%20plea%20for%20help.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EI%20was%20flooded%20with%20relief%20when%20I%20received%20an%20immediate%20reply%20from%20a%20profile%20with%20the%20title%20%26quot%3BCustomer%20Service%26quot%3B.%20The%20person%20on%20the%20other%20end%20asked%20for%20my%20phone%20number%20and%20email%20address%2C%20and%20I%20got%20a%20call%20minutes%20later.%20With%20a%20shaky%20voice%20I%20explained%20what%20was%20going%20on%20and%20the%20voice%20on%20the%20other%20end%20of%20the%20phone%20%E2%80%94%20someone%20named%20Kenneth%20%E2%80%94%20apologized%20for%20the%20error%20and%20said%20he%20could%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20that's%20when%20he%20got%20me.%20I%20was%20so%20desperate%20to%20connect%20with%20a%20live%20person%2C%20that%20I%20was%20willing%20to%20follow%20every%20instruction%20that%20he%20gave%20me%20to%20rectify%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKenneth%20(who%20knows%20if%20that%20was%20even%20his%20name)%20said%20that%20not%20only%20would%20I%20not%20be%20charged%20the%20exorbitant%20fee%20for%20the%20extra%20two%20days%2C%20he%20would%20make%20my%20extra%20two%20days%20complimentary%20just%20for%20my%20trouble.%20All%20I%20needed%20to%20do%20was%20confirm%20my%20credit%20card%20number.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EHe%20said%20for%20safety%20reasons%20I%20shouldn't%20tell%20him%20the%20number%20over%20the%20phone%2C%20but%20instead%20download%20an%20app%20called%20Remitly%20where%20the%20number%20would%20stay%20confidential.%20He%20said%20he%20would%20send%20a%20%24100%20refund%20to%20my%20card%20to%20make%20up%20for%20the%20extra%20two%20days%20I'd%20be%20charged.%20Looking%20back%2C%20I%20now%20realize%20this%20doesn't%20make%20much%20sense%20and%20it%20wasn't%20even%20the%20right%20amount.%20It%20should%20have%20been%20%24102%20if%20he%20was%20crediting%20me%20for%20two%20days.%20But%2C%20I%20didn't%20even%20hesitate%20for%20a%20second.%20No%20warning%20bells%20went%20off%20in%20my%20head%20or%20my%20gut.%20I%20was%20just%20so%20glad%20to%20finally%20be%20getting%20help.%20I%20followed%20his%20instructions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d80e2fa4-cacc-4837-87f0-fce65d90dcaa%5C%22%3EAnd%20then%2C%20it%20happened%20again%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20I%20got%20another%20Facebook%20message%20from%20a%20different%20%26quot%3BCustomer%20Service%26quot%3B%20profile%20stating%20they%20were%20trying%20to%20contact%20me%20but%20I%20wasn't%20picking%20up%20the%20phone.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20OK%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20typed.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20talking%20to%20someone%20right%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHang%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BHang%20up%20the%20phone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20chill%20crept%20over%20me%20from%20head%20to%20toe.%20%26quot%3BOh%20my%20God%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20wrote%20back.%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscammed-out-of-family-savings-in-three-months-painful-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIt's%20a%20scam.%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20just%20gave%20this%20guy%20my%20credit%20card%20number.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20hung%20up%20the%20immediately%20and%20the%20phone%20rang%20again.%20Now%20someone%20allegedly%20name%20James%20was%20available%20to%20help%20me.%20Now%20I%20was%20snapped%20out%20of%20my%20daze%20and%20hung%20up%20on%20him%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228b884a68-5de8-4dde-9af6-7fc7346c833a%5C%22%3EFinally%2C%20I%20heard%20from%20a%20real%20person%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20the%20rental%20car%20company%20wrote%20back%20on%20Facebook%20saying%20none%20of%20the%20messages%20or%20calls%20had%20come%20from%20them%2C%20and%20that%20I'd%20have%20to%20work%20the%20extra%20fees%20out%20at%20the%20rental%20counter%20when%20I%20returned%20the%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20humiliated%20and%20even%20more%20panicked%20now.%20I%20called%20my%20credit%20card%20company%20and%20cancelled%20the%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20the%20next%2036%20hours%20berating%20myself%20for%20being%20so%20foolish.%20When%20I%20arrived%20at%20the%20rental%20car%20counter%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20find%20a%20manager%20who%20cancelled%20the%20%243678.07%20charge%20that%20caused%20me%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20customer%20service%20in%20the%20first%20place%2C%20but%20by%20then%20I%20was%20a%20complete%20wreck.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-grandmother-daisy-scambait-online-scams-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escammers%3C%2Fa%3E%20ended%20up%20charging%20me%20%24100%20and%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20I'll%20ever%20get%20that%20money%20back%2C%20but%20realize%20I'm%20lucky%20that's%20all%20this%20annoying%20lesson%20cost%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22857cce4d-4249-496c-b3f9-17454607b4d3%5C%22%3EI'll%20do%20things%20differently%20next%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20time%20I'm%20up%20against%20a%20stressful%20customer%20service%20issue%2C%20I'll%20remind%20myself%20to%20take%20a%20deep%20breath%20and%20go%20slow.%20When%20I%20feel%20that%20sense%20of%20relief%20that%20someone%20is%20coming%20to%20my%20aid%2C%20I'll%20always%20take%20a%20pause%20and%20verify%20that%20they%20are%20who%20they%20say%20they%20are%2C%20especially%20when%20I'm%20reaching%20out%20via%20social%20media.%20And%20the%20next%20time%20someone%20calls%20me%20cynical%2C%20I'll%20tell%20them%20%26quot%3BIt%20comes%20from%20experience.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmart-but-got-scammed-customer-service-while-traveling-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737109382000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67893c2d50dfd88e193ebfbd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22o