en%2C%20besides%20Rs%205%2C000%20for%20the%20first%20child%20and%20Rs%206%2C000%20for%20the%20second%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20announced%20a%20Mahila%20Smriddhi%20Yojana%20under%20which%20women%20will%20receive%20assistance%20of%20Rs%202%2C500%20per%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20that%20the%20AAP%20had%20promised%20to%20give%20Rs%201%2C000%20to%20women%20in%202021%2C%20Mr%20Nadda%20alleged%20the%20party%20has%20not%20fulfilled%20its%20promises%20-%20neither%20in%20Punjab%20nor%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20will%20also%20provide%20a%20Rs%20500%20subsidy%20on%20LPG%20cylinders%2C%20the%20BJP%20leader%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20people%20will%20also%20receive%20two%20free%20cylinders%20on%20Diwali%20and%20Holi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Nadda%20has%20also%20assured%20that%20if%20the%20BJP%20comes%20to%20power%20in%20Delhi%2C%20it%20will%20enforce%20the%20centre's%20flagship%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20health%20scheme%20in%20its%20first%20cabinet%20meeting.%20The%20AAP%20government%20had%20been%20opposing%20the%20central%20scheme%20stating%20that%20the%20city%20already%20has%20%26quot%3Bsuperior%26quot%3B%20health%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20citizens%20will%20also%20get%20an%20additional%20health%20cover%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%2C%20which%20will%20increase%20the%20total%20health%20cover%20given%20to%20the%20elderly%20to%20Rs%2010%20lakh%2C%20according%20to%20the%20manifesto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20announced%20a%20pension%20scheme%20under%20which%20senior%20citizens%20will%20receive%20Rs%202%2C000-2%2C500%20in%20the%2060-70%20age%20group%20and%203%2C000%20Rs%20for%20those%20above%2070.%20For%20the%20Divyang%20and%20widow%2C%20the%20assistance%20will%20be%20increased%20to%20Rs%203%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtal%20Canteens%20will%20be%20set%20up%20in%20every%20slum%20where%20a%20full%20meal%20can%20be%20availed%20at%20just%20Rs%205%2C%20he%20promised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Nadda%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the