en.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f1974c9b-0758-463a-aa50-f4dc1e6b0f4d%5C%22%3EThe%20Palisades%20fire%20ignited%20for%20several%20reasons%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20would%20never%20envision%20an%20entire%20community%20burning%2C%20but%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwildfires-los-angeles-lahaina-paradise-weather-cause-climate-crisis-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewildfires%20were%20born%20from%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20perfect%20storm%20of%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIncreasing%20average%20temperatures%20put%20stress%20on%20vegetation%20in%20the%20mountains%20that%20hadn't%20burned%20in%2030%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExtremely%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-la-los-angeles-fires-wildfires-updates-pacific-palisades-eaton-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh%20wind%20speeds%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20played%20a%20major%20role.%20The%20winds%20carried%20embers%20a%20mile%20from%20the%20wildfire%2C%20blowtorching%20flames%20out%20of%20the%20mountains%20and%20into%20flat%2C%20more%20urban%20areas.%20In%20those%20areas%2C%20houses%2C%20fences%2C%20and%20vegetation%20were%20already%20burning%20well%20ahead%20of%20the%20fire's%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20also%20human-caused%20factors.%20Fire%20departments%20and%20responders%20ran%20out%20of%20water%2C%20so%20fire%20suppression%20that%20would%20normally%20occur%20on%20the%20ground%20ceased%20for%20a%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFires%20in%20this%20area%20are%20also%20typically%20attacked%20from%20the%20air%20with%20airplanes%20and%20helicopters.%20However%2C%20those%20aircraft%20were%20grounded%20due%20to%20the%20high%20winds%2C%20preventing%20the%20use%20of%20fire%20retardants%20and%20other%20aerial%20suppression%20methods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223ea5eadd-8125-46f5-95d2-257a959eceb9%5C%22%3EI%20don't%20plan%20to%20leave%20the%20Palisades%2C%20but%20I've%20taken%20steps%20to%20protect%20my%20house%20and%20family%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20absolutely%20plan%20to%20continue%20living%20in%20the%20Palisades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20scientist%20and%20a%20fourth-generation%20Californian%2C%20wildfire%20risk%20is%20always%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20my%20mind.%20I've%20mitigated%20everything%20I%20could%20around%20my%20property%2C%20from%20installing%20double-paned%20windows%20and%20a%20fire-resistant%20roof.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20house%20is%20anchored%20in%20bedrock%2C%20so%20my%20earthquake%20risk%20is%20relatively%20low.%20Plus%2C%20I%20live%20high%20enough%20above%20the%20Pacific%20Ocean%20that%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20sea%20level%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Howard%20Botts%20pool%20with%20debris%20from%20the%20Pacific%20Palisades%20wildfires.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67868786e294a7514e8ced6d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBotts'%20pool%20has%20some%20debris%20from%20the%20Palisades%20fire.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Howard%20Botts%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EConversely%2C%20it%20will%20take%20a%20decade%20for%20my%20community%20to%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20older%20homes%20likely%20had%20asbestos%20or%20lead%2C%20requiring%20major%20remediation%20efforts%2C%20including%20removing%20soil%20and%20other%20materials.%20This%20will%20prevent%20people%20from%20moving%20back%20in%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20the%20stores%2C%20banks%2C%20post%20offices%2C%20and%20schools%20are%20all%20gone%2C%20so%20any%20sense%20of%20community%20closeness%20is%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20be%20a%20long%20time%20before%20this%20area%20bounces%20back%20%E2%80%94%20that%20will%20be%20the%20real%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2289d55d34-ea46-48c0-a248-d73ca4155337%5C%22%3EInsurance%20costs%20could%20impact%20whether%20people%20who%20lost%20homes%20rebuild%20or%20move%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Palisades%20is%20relatively%20affluent.%20However%2C%20the%20areas%20affected%20by%20the%20Eaton%20fire%20have%20many%20more%20middle-class%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20fires%20will%20change%20the%20character%20of%20those%20neighborhoods%2C%20because%20the%20key%20question%20is%2C%20%26quot%3BCan%20residents%20afford%20to%20rebuild%20at%20the%20cost%20it%20will%20take%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuilding%20codes%20have%20changed%2C%20so%20homes%20being%20rebuilt%20will%20need%20to%20meet%20the%20latest%20standards%2C%20including%20indoor%20sprinklers%20for%20fire%20suppression%20and%20fireproof%20Class%20A%20roofs%2C%20which%20will%20increase%20both%20materials%20and%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20question%20is%2C%20%26quot%3BDo%20residents%20have%20enough%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-fire-insurance-coverage-cancellation-no-payout-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einsurance%20coverage%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20make%20rebuilding%20possible%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225808%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22tesla%20parked%20in%20the%20driveway%20of%20a%20standing%20house%20next%20to%20a%20burning%20house%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6780520550dfd88e193dbdfc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223872%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20structure%20burns%20in%20the%20Pacific%20Palisades%20neighborhood%20of%20Los%20Angeles.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FEtienne%20Laurent%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECalifornia%20definitely%20has%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flos-angeles-la-neighborhoods-fires-pacific-palisades-home-insurance-rollbacks-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einsurability%20problem%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20a%20major%20insurer%20did%20not%20renew%20my%20policy.%20The%20only%20fire%20insurance%20I%20could%20get%20was%20through%20the%20California%20FAIR%20Plan%2