0From%20January%2017%3A%20What%20It%20Means%20For%20Indian%20Professionals%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20is%20introducing%20significant%20changes%20to%20its%20H-1B%20visa%20programme%20starting%20Friday%2C%20January%2017.%20The%20updated%20regulations%2C%20to%20allow%20highly%20skilled%20workers%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20US%20based%20on%20their%20employment%20status%2C%20form%20one%20of%20the%20final%20immigration%20policy%20reforms%20under%20the%20outgoing%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20H-1B%20visa%20programme%2C%20which%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20attracting%20global%20talent%2C%20will%20undergo%20a%20series%20of%20updates%20designed%20to%20modernise%20its%20framework%20and%20address%20current%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.uscis.gov%2Fnewsroom%2Falerts%2Fh-1b-final-rule-h-2-final-rule-and-revised-form-i-129-effective-jan-17-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnited%20States%20Citizenship%20and%20Immigration%20Services%3C%2Fa%3E%20(USCIS)%20stated%20on%20its%20website%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20H-1B%20final%20rule%20modernizes%20the%20H-1B%20program%20by%20streamlining%20the%20approval%20process%2C%20increasing%20its%20flexibility%20to%20allow%20better%20employers%20to%20retain%20talented%20workers%2C%20and%20improving%20the%20integrity%20and%20oversight%20of%20the%20program.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Indian%20professionals%20comprising%20over%2070%20percent%20of%20H-1B%20visa%20holders%20in%202023%2C%20these%20changes%20could%20substantially%20benefit%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKey%20Changes%20To%20H-1B%20Visa%20Rules%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Specialty%20occupation'%20definition%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20new%20rule%20updates%20the%20definition%20of%20%E2%80%9Cspeciality%20occupation%E2%80%9D%20by%20revising%20the%20criteria%20for%20eligible%20positions.%20It%20clarifies%20that%20a%20degree%20requirement%20is%20%E2%80%9Cnormally%E2%80%9D%20needed%2C%20not%20%E2%80%9Calways%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20allows%20a%20broader%20range%20of%20qualifying%20degrees%2C%20as%20long%20as%20they%20are%20directly%20related%20to%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFairer%20lottery%20process%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EStricter%20measures%20will%20curb%20organisations%20submitting%20multiple%20bulk%20applications%2C%20ensuring%20a%20more%20equitable%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESimplified%20transition%20for%20F-1%20visa%20holders%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EStudents%20with%20F-1%20visas%20will%20experience%20fewer%20challenges%20when%20moving%20to%20H-1B%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFaster%20processing%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EUSCIS%20will%20expedite%20H-1B%20extension%20applications%2C%20reducing%20delays%20for%20workers%20and%20employers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMore%20flexibility%20for%20employers%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECompanies%20can%20hire%20H-1B%20workers%20based%20on%20their%20specific%20workforce%20needs%2C%20supporting%20dynamic%20workforce%20planning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOpportunities%20for%20entrepreneurs%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEntrepreneurs%20owning%20a%20majority%20stake%20in%20their%20company%20can%20now%20self-petition%20for%20H-1B%20visas%2C%20provided%20they%20meet%20stricter%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStronger%20compliance%20safeguards%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEnhanced%20site%20visit%20authority%20for%20USCIS%2C%20including%20inspections%20at%20worksites%2C%20remote%20locations%2C%20and%20third-party%20sites%20aim%20to%20deter%20misuse.%20Failure%20to%20verify%20information%20during%20inspections%20may%20lead%20to%20denial%20or%20revocation%20of%20H-1B%20petitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20petition%20form%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20newly%20updated%20Form%20I-129%20will%20be%20mandatory%20starting%20January%2017%2C%202025%2C%20for%20improved%20compliance.%20This%2