e%20of%20the%20guidelines%20directly%20impacts%20them.%20The%20guidelines%20did%20not%20name%20a%20single%20cricketer%20but%20here's%20a%20look%20at%20how%20the%20new%20rules%20can%20end%20up%20affecting%20the%20three%20senior%20members%20of%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20point%20of%20the%20guidelines%20states%20that%20%26quot%3BParticipation%20in%20Domestic%20Matches%20is%20mandatory%20for%20players%20to%20remain%20eligible%20for%20selection%20in%20the%20national%20team%20and%20for%20central%20contracts.%20Any%20exceptions%20to%20this%20mandate%20will%20be%20considered%20only%20under%20extraordinary%20circumstances%20and%20will%20require%20formal%20notification%20and%20approval%20from%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Selection%20Committee%2C%20ensuring%20fairness%20and%20transparency%20in%20the%20process%26quot%3B.%20The%20three%20seniors%20have%20not%20played%20domestic%20cricket%20for%20quite%20some%20time%20-%20Rohit%20last%20played%20in%202016%2C%20Bumrah%20in%202018%20and%20Virat%20played%20his%20last%20game%20for%20Delhi%20way%20back%20in%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20point%20makes%20it%20clear%20that%20%26quot%3BAll%20players%20are%20expected%20to%20travel%20with%20the%20team%20to%20and%20from%20matches%20and%20practice%20sessions.%20Separate%20travel%20arrangements%20with%20families%20are%20discouraged%20to%20maintain%20discipline%20and%20team%20cohesion%26quot%3B.%20This%20is%20also%20an%20issue%20for%20the%20senior%20as%20Virat%20rarely%20travels%20with%20the%20team%20since%20Covid-19.%20Even%20during%20the%20Australia%20series%2C%20Virat%20and%20Bumrah%20travelled%20separately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Point%20No.%204%2C%20%26quot%3BPersonal%20staff%20(e.g.%2C%20personal%20managers%2C%20chefs%2C%20assistants%20and%20security)%20are%20to%20be%20restricted%20on%20tours%20or%20series%20unless%20explicitly%20approved%20by%20the%20BCCI%26quot%3B.%20While%20nothing%20official%20is%20known%20about%20the%20trio's%20entourage%2C%20it%20will%20certainly%20affect%20their%20travel%20with%20the%20team%20going%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBCCI%20said%20that%20-%20%26quot%3BPlayers%20are%20not%20permitted%20to%20engage%20in%20personal%20shoots%20or%20endorsements%20during%20an%20ongoing%20series%20or%20tour%26quot%3B.%20Considering%20the%20popularity%20and%20commitments%20of%20the%20three%20star%20cricketers%2C%20this%20can%20prove%20to%20be%20a%20major%20issue%20and%20may%20even%20impact%20their%20brand%20endorsements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20guidelines%20regarding%20cricketers'%20families%20state%20that%20%26quot%3BPlayers%20absent%20from%20India%20for%20more%20than%2045%20days%20during%20overseas%20tours%20can%20be%20joined%20by%20their%20partners%20and%20children%20(under%2018)%20for%20one%20visit%20per%20series%20(format-wise)%20of%20up%20to%20a%20two-week%20period%26quot%3B.%20In%20the%20recent%20past%2C%20Rohit%2C%20Bumrah%20and%20Virat%20have%20all%20travelled%20with%20their%20families%20and%20this%20rule%20will%20most%20certainly%20impact%20the%20three%20senior%20stars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlayers%20are%20required%20to%20stay%20with%20the%20team%20until%20the%20scheduled%20end%20of%20the%20match%20series%20or%20tour%2C%20regardless%20of%20whether%20matches%20conclude%20earlier%20than%20planned%2C%26quot%3B%20BCCI%20said.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20senior%20players%20have%20returned%20home%20early%20when%20the%20matches%20ended%20but%20that%20will%20change%20due%20to%20the%20new%20guidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737098460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Feabop7fg_sac_625x300_17_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fbccis-10-point-diktat-what-the-new-rules-mean-for-rohit-sharma-virat-kohli-and-jasprit-bumrah-7493924%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BCCI%20came%20up%20with%2010-point%20guidelines%20for%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20following%20the%20Test%20series