3EThe%20impact%20goes%20beyond%20just%20improving%20attendance.%20The%20team%20has%20distributed%20over%203%2C000%20bags%2C%20saving%20over%2070%20million%20litres%20of%20water%2C%20preventing%2058%2C000%20kg%20of%20carbon%20emissions%2C%20and%20upcycling%20more%20than%203%2C600%20kg%20of%20textile%20waste.%20These%20figures%20aren%E2%80%99t%20just%20numbers%2C%20they%20represent%20real%20change%2C%20opportunities%2C%20and%20hope%20for%20those%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EScaling%20up%20the%20mission%3A%20Threads4Good%E2%80%99s%20plans%20for%20the%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2017-year-old%20initially%20funded%20the%20initiative%20using%20his%20personal%20savings%2C%20but%20he%20needed%20more%20funds%20to%20expand%20it.%20Currently%2C%20there%20are%20around%2026%20disabled%20individuals%20and%2013%20marginalised%20women%20working%20for%20the%20initiative.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20faced%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F346172%2Fblind-german-woman-sabriye-tenberken-founded-kanthari-start-ngo-tibetan-script-braille-without-borders%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echallenge%20of%20fundraising%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20we%20needed%20money%20to%20pay%20the%20people%20who%20made%20the%20bags%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20solved%20this%20problem%20with%20grants%20and%20award%20money.%E2%80%9D%20Among%20the%20grants%20and%20awards%20that%20supported%20the%20project%20are%20the%20Diana%20Award%20(2024)%2C%20the%20Ashoka%20Seed%20Prize%20(Rs%2030%2C000)%2C%20the%20International%20Young%20Eco-Hero%20Award%20(USD%201%2C000)%2C%20and%20the%20Harvard%20Impact%20Initiative%20Award.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20young%20founder%20has%20ambitious%20plans%20for%20the%20future%2C%20including%20filing%20a%20Public%20Interest%20Litigation%20(PIL)%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20government%20takes%20responsibility%20for%20ensuring%20proper%20attendance%20in%20governme